import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
In [ ]:
results = pd.read_csv("./results.csv")
faultless = results[results["probability"].isna()]
faulty = results[results["probability"].notna()]

# GENERAL
faultless_rw = faultless[faultless["algorithm_type"] == "RANDOM"]
faulty_rw_c_0001 = faulty[(faulty["algorithm_type"] == "RANDOM") & (faulty["nodes"] < faulty["robots"]) & (faulty["probability"] == 0.001)]
faulty_rw_c_0010 = faulty[(faulty["algorithm_type"] == "RANDOM") & (faulty["nodes"] < faulty["robots"]) & (faulty["probability"] == 0.01)]
faulty_rw_c_0100 = faulty[(faulty["algorithm_type"] == "RANDOM") & (faulty["nodes"] < faulty["robots"]) & (faulty["probability"] == 0.1)]
faulty_rw_c_1000 = faulty[(faulty["algorithm_type"] == "RANDOM") & (faulty["nodes"] < faulty["robots"]) & (faulty["probability"] == 1)]
faulty_rw_p_0001 = faulty[(faulty["algorithm_type"] == "RANDOM") & (faulty["nodes"] >= faulty["robots"]) & (faulty["probability"] == 0.001)]
faulty_rw_p_0010 = faulty[(faulty["algorithm_type"] == "RANDOM") & (faulty["nodes"] >= faulty["robots"]) & (faulty["probability"] == 0.01)]
faulty_rw_p_0100 = faulty[(faulty["algorithm_type"] == "RANDOM") & (faulty["nodes"] >= faulty["robots"]) & (faulty["probability"] == 0.1)]
faulty_rw_p_1000 = faulty[(faulty["algorithm_type"] == "RANDOM") & (faulty["nodes"] >= faulty["robots"]) & (faulty["probability"] == 1)]

random_dict = {
    'F_0000': faultless_rw["steps"].mean(),
    'C_0001': faulty_rw_c_0001["steps"].mean(),
    'C_0010': faulty_rw_c_0010["steps"].mean(),
    'C_0100': faulty_rw_c_0100["steps"].mean(),
    'C_1000': faulty_rw_c_1000["steps"].mean(),
    'P_0001': faulty_rw_p_0001["steps"].mean(),
    'P_0010': faulty_rw_p_0010["steps"].mean(),
    'P_0100': faulty_rw_p_0100["steps"].mean(),
    'P_1000': faulty_rw_p_1000["steps"].mean()
}

faultsless_rr = faultless[faultless["algorithm_type"] == "ROTOR_ROUTER"]
faulty_rr_c_0001 = faulty[(faulty["algorithm_type"] == "ROTOR_ROUTER") & (faulty["nodes"] < faulty["robots"]) & (faulty["probability"] == 0.001)]
faulty_rr_c_0010 = faulty[(faulty["algorithm_type"] == "ROTOR_ROUTER") & (faulty["nodes"] < faulty["robots"]) & (faulty["probability"] == 0.01)]
faulty_rr_c_0100 = faulty[(faulty["algorithm_type"] == "ROTOR_ROUTER") & (faulty["nodes"] < faulty["robots"]) & (faulty["probability"] == 0.1)]
faulty_rr_c_1000 = faulty[(faulty["algorithm_type"] == "ROTOR_ROUTER") & (faulty["nodes"] < faulty["robots"]) & (faulty["probability"] == 1)]
faulty_rr_p_0001 = faulty[(faulty["algorithm_type"] == "ROTOR_ROUTER") & (faulty["nodes"] >= faulty["robots"]) & (faulty["probability"] == 0.001)]
faulty_rr_p_0010 = faulty[(faulty["algorithm_type"] == "ROTOR_ROUTER") & (faulty["nodes"] >= faulty["robots"]) & (faulty["probability"] == 0.01)]
faulty_rr_p_0100 = faulty[(faulty["algorithm_type"] == "ROTOR_ROUTER") & (faulty["nodes"] >= faulty["robots"]) & (faulty["probability"] == 0.1)]
faulty_rr_p_1000 = faulty[(faulty["algorithm_type"] == "ROTOR_ROUTER") & (faulty["nodes"] >= faulty["robots"]) & (faulty["probability"] == 1)]

rotor_dict = {
    'F_0000': faultsless_rr["steps"].mean(),
    'C_0001': faulty_rr_c_0001["steps"].mean(),
    'C_0010': faulty_rr_c_0010["steps"].mean(),
    'C_0100': faulty_rr_c_0100["steps"].mean(),
    'C_1000': faulty_rr_c_1000["steps"].mean(),
    'P_0001': faulty_rr_p_0001["steps"].mean(),
    'P_0010': faulty_rr_p_0010["steps"].mean(),
    'P_0100': faulty_rr_p_0100["steps"].mean(),
    'P_1000': faulty_rr_p_1000["steps"].mean()
}

# create two subplots
fig, (ax1, ax2) = plt.subplots(ncols=2, figsize=(20, 5))

# plot the first dictionary
ax1.bar(random_dict.keys(), random_dict.values())
ax1.set_title("Random Walk")
for i, v in random_dict.items():
    ax1.text(i, v, str(v), ha='center', va='bottom')

# plot the second dictionary
ax2.bar(rotor_dict.keys(), rotor_dict.values())
ax2.set_title("Rotor Router")
for i, v in rotor_dict.items():
    ax2.text(i, v, str(v), ha='center', va='bottom')

# adjust spacing between subplots
plt.tight_layout()

# show the plot
plt.show()
